description:
he product is a ready-mix concrete consisting of aggregates, cement OPC,
GGBS, Water and Additive.
The strength class of the product is 50 MPa at 28 days.
Typical physical properties for the product:
Density: 2401.7 kg/m3
Free Water/cement ratio: 0.35
The product complies with BS 8500-1 & Authority requirements, Circular
225 - Dubai Municipality.
Further information can be found at www.readymixgulf.ae
